<Body>
	<Title>北京幼儿园校餐致近50名儿童中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007年9月7日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">新京报</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">9月7日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">信息</Denoter>：(记者展明辉 葛江涛)</Event></Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">昨日下午</Time>，<Location lid="l2">北京市昌平区回龙观镇西半壁店村一幼儿园</Location>，<Participant sid="s2">近50名儿童</Participant>和<Participant sid="s2">3名老师</Participant>因食用未煮熟的扁豆而<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e3"><Denoter did="d3" type="operation">入院</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">事发</Denoter></Event>后，<Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5" type="agent">昌平区政府</Participant>、<Participant sid="s5" type="agent">教委</Participant>、<Participant sid="s5" type="agent">卫生局</Participant>、<Participant sid="s5" type="agent">公安</Participant>等部门联合行动<Denoter did="d5" type="operation">救助</Denoter><Participant oid="o5" type="recipient">患者</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e6">并将<Participant oid="o6" type="recipient">该校负责人</Participant>和<Participant oid="o6" type="recipient">厨师</Participant><Denoter did="d" type="operation">控制</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e7"><Time tid="t7" type="relTime">目前</Time>，<Object oid="o7">事件</Object>正在<Denoter did="d7" type="operation">调查</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>出事的学校为汉硕双语幼儿教育基地，属私人办学。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e8"><Time tid="t8" type="relTime">8月27日</Time>，<Participant sid="s8">该校</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="operation">开学</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">100多名学生</Participant>陆续<Denoter did="d9" type="movement">返校</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e10"><Denoter did="d10" type="operation">上课</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e11">据<Participant sid="s11">家长们</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12">大部分孩子</Participant>一般在<Location lid="l12">学校</Location><Denoter did="d12" type="action">吃</Denoter><Object oid="o12">午饭</Object>和<Object oid="o12">晚饭</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e13"><Object oid="o13">两顿</Object>均由校方聘请的<Participant sid="s13">厨师</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="operation">制作</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>昨日午饭的内容为米饭、肉炒扁豆、炒黄瓜和西红柿鸡蛋汤。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e14"><Time tid="t14" type="relTime">昨日下午2时许</Time>，有<Participant sid="s14">8名孩子</Participant><Denoter did="d14" type="action">睡午觉</Denoter></Event>时，<Event eid="e15">陆续<Denoter did="d15" type="stateChange">产生</Denoter>了恶心、呕吐等<Object oid="o15">症状</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e16"><Time tid="t16" type="relTime">随后</Time>，<Participant sid="s16">更多人</Participant><Denoter did="d16" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter><Object oid="o16">不适</Object></Event>。<Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17" type="agent">校方</Participant>遂<Denoter did="d17" type="operation">联系</Denoter><Participant  oid="o17" type="recipient">医院</Participant></Event><Event eid="e18">开始<Denoter did="d18" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>“<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">我们</Participant>大人都不知道这事，到<Denoter did="d19" type="action">接</Denoter><Participant oid="o19">孩子</Participant>回家的时候</Event><Event eid="e20">才<Denoter did="d20" type="perception">发现</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e21"><Participant sid="s21">人</Participant>都<Denoter did="d21" type="stateChange">不见</Denoter>了</Event>。”<Event eid="e22"><Participant sid="s22">家长们</Participant><Denoter did="d22" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e23"><Time tid="t23" type="relTime">昨日下午4时许</Time>，<Participant oid="o23">近50名学生</Participant>已经被<Denoter did="d23" type="action">接到</Denoter>了<Location lid="l23">沙河医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e24"><Denoter did="d24" type="operation">抢救</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e25">另有<Participant sid="s25">数十名孩子</Participant><Denoter did="d25" type="action">留在</Denoter><Location lid="l25">幼儿园内</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e26">接受赶来的<Participant sid="s26">医生</Participant><Denoter did="d26" type="operation">检查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>此外，<Event eid="e27">还有<Participant sid="s27">3名老师</Participant>也发生<Denoter did="d27" type="action">呕吐</Denoter>情况</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>“听说都是扁豆没煮熟闹的，厨师还是刚来的。”<Event eid="e28"><Participant sid="s28">家长们</Participant><Denoter did="d28" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e29"><Time tid="t29" type="relTime">昨晚8时30分许</Time>，<Object oid="o29">汉硕双语幼儿教育基地大门</Object><Denoter did="d29" type="action">紧闭</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e30"><Location lid="l30">外面</Location><Denoter did="d30" type="action">停</Denoter>有一辆留守的回龙观镇医院<Object oid="o30">救护车</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e31"><Time tid="t" type="relTime">此时</Time>，<Participant oid="o31">孩子们</Participant>已全部被<Denoter did="d31" type="movement">送走</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e32"><Participant oid="o32" type="recipient">校方工作人员</Participant>仍在接受<Participant sid="s32" type="agent">卫生监督所人员</Participant><Denoter did="d32" type="action">询问</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e33"><Time tid="t33" type="relTime">昨晚10时许</Time>，在父母的陪伴下，<Participant oid="o33">十几名儿童</Participant>仍在<Location lid="l33">沙河医院观察室内</Location>打点滴<Denoter did="d33" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e34">据<Participant sid="s34">院方</Participant><Denoter did="d34" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，所有患者症状稳定，没有危重患者。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e35">据<Participant sid="s35">昌平区政府工作人员</Participant>介绍<Denoter did="d35" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e36"><Denoter did="d36" type="emergency">事</Denoter>发</Event>后，<Event eid="e37"><Participant sid="s37">他们</Participant>立即<Denoter did="d37" type="operation">启动</Denoter><Object oid="o37">突发事件应急预案</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e38"><Participant sid="s38">区领导</Participant>和<Participant sid="s38">教委、卫生局、疾病控制中心、工商分局、公安局等单位人员</Participant><Denoter did="d38" type="movement">前往</Denoter><Location lid="l38" type="destination">现场</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e39">对<Object oid="o39">此事</Object>展开<Denoter did="d39" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e40">并对<Participant oid="o40" type="recipient">该校全部儿童</Participant>进行身体<Denoter did="d40" type="operation">检查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e41">据<Participant sid="s41">该工作人员</Participant><Denoter did="d41" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，由于现场已无剩余食品，<Event eid="e42"><Participant sid="s42">调查人员</Participant><Denoter did="d42" type="operation">采集</Denoter>了相关的<Object oid="o42">用具</Object>和<Object oid="o42">食品容器</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e43"><Denoter did="d43" type="movement">送</Denoter><Location lid="l43" type="destination">区疾病预防控制中心</Location></Event><Event eid="e44"><Denoter did="d44" type="operation">检验</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>经现场了解，<Event eid="e45"><Participant sid="s45">全部患者</Participant>都在<Location lid="l45">幼儿园</Location>中<Denoter did="d45" type="action">用餐</Denoter></Event>，初步判断为夹生扁豆引起的食物中毒。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e46">据<Participant sid="s46">昌平区有关部门</Participant><Denoter did="d46" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>，汉硕双语幼儿教育基地属于汉硕文化发展有限公司，<Event eid="e47"><Participant sid="s47">该公司</Participant>在<Location lid="l47">海淀区</Location><Denoter did="d47" type="operation">注册</Denoter></Event>，在昌平属于非法办学。</Sentence><Sentence>该校食堂未取得卫生许可证，擅自供餐。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e48"><Participant sid="s48">食堂厨师</Participant><Denoter did="d48" type="movement">来自</Denoter><Location lid="l48">安徽</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e49">在<Location lid="l49">西城区</Location><Denoter did="d49" type="action">取得</Denoter><Object oid="o49">上岗证</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e50"><Time tid="t50" type="relTime">9月4日</Time>刚刚<Denoter did="d50" type="movement">进校</Denoter>工作</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e51"><Time tid="t51" type="relTime">目前</Time>，<Participant sid="s51" type="agent">警方</Participant>和<Participant sid="s51" type="agent">卫生局</Participant>已将<Participant oid="o51" type="recipient">该公司负责人</Participant>和<Participant oid="o51" type="recipient">当事厨师</Participant><Denoter did="d51" type="operation">控制</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e52">对<Object oid="o52">该校</Object><Denoter did="d52" type="operation">采取</Denoter><Object oid="o52">行政控制措施</Object></Event>.</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
